          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "成其百年之好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，众鬼卒！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（大鬼卒、四小鬼同应声。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼卒、四小鬼",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔！"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一壁厢准备笙箫鼓乐，一壁厢准备琴剑书箱，随爷嫁妹走遭。带蹇驴！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼卒、四小鬼",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "钟馗 （粉蝶儿） 摆列着破伞孤灯，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "对着这平安吉庆；"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乘着这蹇驴儿趷蹬。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "似一幅梅花春兴。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "钟馗→四小鬼",
          "turns": 2
        },
        {
          "edge": "四小鬼→钟馗",
          "turns": 1
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
