    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "大鬼卒",
        "梅香",
        "钟妹",
        "钟馗"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（大鬼卒、四小鬼引钟馗同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（石榴花） 俺只见枝头鸟语弄轻声，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小桥边残雪报春晴。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与骚人才子添诗兴。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（石榴花） 今来古往有许多评论。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼卒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "已到村口。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "带住蹇驴！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼卒、四小鬼",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔！"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你等村口伺候，一唤即至！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼卒、四小鬼",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（大鬼卒、四小鬼自两边分下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（合头） 趁着这月色微明，"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（合头） 又只见门庭冷落倍伤情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是自家门首。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹子开门来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟妹",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖起定更鼓〗。钟妹上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "钟妹 （泣颜回） 听樵楼早已报初更，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刁斗无声寂静。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是何人叩我柴门？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "钟馗 （夹白） 愚兄回来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "钟妹 （泣颜回） 我闻言战惊，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丧黄泉复现生时影。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹子不要害怕，就是你哥哥钟馗回来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，既是哥哥回来，妹子焉能害怕，待我与你开门。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（钟妹开门。钟馗进入。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹子在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥哥在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗、钟妹",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，（妹子）（哥哥）呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "钟妹 （泣颜回） 兄和妹手足关情，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "却为何改变容形？"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗、钟妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗、钟妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥哥可将别后之事说与小妹知道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹子听了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄龙滚） 想当初自离门庭，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到中途瘧妖作症。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "改变了旧日容颜赴帝京；"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昏君呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄龙滚） 将俺来黜落功名，"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一时愤怒！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄龙滚） 后宰门捐躯殒命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不知何人将哥哥尸骸埋葬？"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多蒙杜大郎将俺尸骸埋葬，感他大恩，未曾报得。向在京师曾将我妹许配于他，"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为此今晚，特备笙箫鼓乐，将我妹送往到彼，与他成其百年之好。不知你心"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "意如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥哥此言差矣！"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何差？"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥哥呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（千秋岁） 论婚姻从古须媒证，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "圣贤言礼法须遵。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仓卒里苟合难以从命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（梅香提灯上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "梅香 （千秋岁） 夜深沉人声静，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "通宵聒絮剔起残灯。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（梅香见钟馗面貌，吓倒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "梅香休得害怕，这是我钟馗哥哥回来了。向前见过你钟老爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "梅香与钟老爷叩头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不消。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，妹子，这是何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是杜大郎送来陪伴小妹的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹子，你方才言道无有媒证，如今就把这小娘子呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（扑灯蛾） 权当个冰人系赤绳，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "权当作斧柯媒证。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "算不得御沟红叶往来情。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "凭与他五百年前石上桔三生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，小妹遵命了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹子请到后面更衣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（梅香扶钟妹同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众鬼卒！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（大鬼卒、四小鬼自两边分上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼卒、四小鬼",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔！"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与俺冠带伺候！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼卒、四小鬼",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（钟馗下，大鬼卒、四小鬼同作舞。〖小工调工尺上〗。钟馗换红官衣执扇上，作舞。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺钟馗今日嫁妹，好不洒乐人也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哧嘻嘻，哧嘻嘻，呵哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（越凭好） 与俺把——"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "敲象板鼍鼓凤笙；"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "暖溶溶香蔼蔼百媚自生。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "后本中裁一个弱质娉婷。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（梅香、钟妹同乘车下，大鬼卒、四小鬼引钟馗同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
