    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "大鬼卒",
        "杜平",
        "梅香",
        "钟馗"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杜平上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杜平 （上小楼） 看皎皎月色明，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寂悄悄人声静。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下官杜平。适才与众家弟兄宴罢而归。看今夜月色溶溶，不免在此闲步一番！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（上小楼） 最喜这月色如银，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "月光如水，月圆如镜。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖内乐声〗。〖节节高〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（上小楼） 听何处箫鼓喧声，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乱纷纷马嘶人影。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（大鬼卒、四小鬼引钟馗同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼卒、四小鬼",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同红绣鞋） 车轮伊哑连声，连声。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马蹄步似流星，流星。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "香馥郁，气氤氲。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "顷刻间，到门庭。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（钟馗上高台。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杜恩兄请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊？空中有人讲话，莫非是鬼魅妖邪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺非鬼魅妖邪，乃终南山进士钟馗，生前受你大恩，未曾报得，为此今晚，特"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "备笙箫鼓乐，将我妹送到府中，成共百年之好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既是钟兄到此，就该请来叙话。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢！你我幽明相隔，后会有期，那旁小妹车辆来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（梅香扶钟妹同上，在钟馗的〖叠子犯〗歌唱中，与杜平同拜天地。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "钟馗 （叠子犯） 哎灿——"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎闪——"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闪的鬼旗掩映；"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎挨——"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "从今后斩妖除魅志平生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟馗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（大鬼卒、四小鬼引钟馗同下，梅香、钟妹、杜平同下。）⑴"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "——————————"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "⑴ 原本，梅香、钟妹在钟馗唱完〖叠子犯〗下场后，始行上场与杜见面，现将原本该段附录于后，以供参考："
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖到春来〗。梅香扶钟妹同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "员外爷开门来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何人叩门？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杜平开门，梅香进入。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "梅香与员外爷叩头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "梅香，我命你去服侍钟小姐，为何夤夜到此？"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉钟老爷之命，送小姐到此与员外爷成亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦？小姐现在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现在门外。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快快有请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请小姐。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（钟妹进入，杜平相迎。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "钟妹 （同尾声） 丝罗幸托终身订，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "百岁良缘天配成。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（梅香、钟妹同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，妙哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（尾声） 六礼还须百辆迎。"
        }
      ],
